graph LR
    LMEval["lm-evaluation-harness<br/>(Batch Job)"]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies
    LMEval -->|"Job orchestration<br/>creates/manages Jobs"| TrustyAI["trustyai-service-operator"]

